---
title: Cal Smart Roasted Salmon with Veggie Bulgur and Lemon Aioli
description: This light and bright meal of seasoned salmon fillets is simplicity at its best! It's finished with a dollop of lemon aioli and served on a savoury bed of roasted zucchini and peppers tossed with bulgur.

Calorie Smart is based on a per serving calculation of the recipe's kilocalorie amount.
